 make a difference every day. Happy International WOMEN'S DAY MnCH FOLLOW US ON in f pkrartscollege www.pkrarts.ac.in\".","caption":{"pk":"18110846209708374","text":"Behind Every Success Story, There is a Woman of Strength.\nHonoring the Achievements and Spirit of Women,Celebrate Her Strength, Courage, and Dreams.\nA woman is the full circle. Within her is the power to create, nurture, and transform\nPKR College Celebrates Women Who Inspire, Lead, and Achieve. \nWishing an International women's day to everyone women.\n\n#internationalwomensday #pkrartscollege #gobichettipalayam #braveness"},"audience":null,"carousel_media_count":null,"display_uri":"https:\/\/instagram.fcjb3-4.fna.fbcdn.net\/v\/t51.82787-15\/642883977_18038734031762532_2196786465919591258_n.webp?stp=c0.240.1440.1440a_dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh0.08_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.fcjb3-4.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2QFlCzLc9yvfr_TBnQO2EzVwjGvXygqgF5kdMgBuJI8Gzv8wIXiWUZiuM7NA6OLG2xEtkeCeloi2eugtIfuh6JCE&_nc_ohc=3pzF2K126xQQ7kNvwFsPoBR&_nc_gid=wNHaFoB5IrIQQNichBjjzQ&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AfwJZH0ho_zY5yXXTT1W_aSgFC3MJjUoDzuDYez-eOOwNQ&oe=69B9F5DD&_nc_sid=10d13b","media_type":1,"carousel_media":null,"image_versions2":{"candidates":[{"height":1921,"url":"https:\/\/instagram.fcjb3-4.fna.fbcdn.net\/v\/t51.82787-15\/642883977_18038734031762532_2196786465919591258_n.webp?_nc_cat=101&ig_cache_key=Mzg0ODAyNzA2NDg2ODI2MDUyNQ\u00253D\u00253D.3-ccb7-5&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=58cdad&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMS5zZHIuQzMifQ\u00253D\u00253D&_nc_ohc=5yKYD7uaINUQ7kNvwHOZQ-u&_nc_oc=AdlXNER50aQdAzNG4L3sgjboU6J9sxagCa9ysjRaG0aP_IPNIx3YHktsSk77IbKhMZqFtg6B4OSqa66V5Xm291EB&_nc_ad=z-m&_nc_cid=1174&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=instagram.fcjb3-4.fna&_nc_gid=wNHaFoB5IrIQQNichBjjzQ&_nc_ss=8&oh=00_Afz2wz2hwiXn6NbCAuMLZyf_8fHuSw97dyjocZsce9NPqw&oe=69B9F5DD","width":1440},{"height":1441,"url":"https:\/\/instagram.fcjb3-4.fna.fbcdn.net\/v\/t51.82787-15\/642883977_18038734031762532_2196786465919591258_n.webp?stp=dst-webp_p1080x108